# Optional per-app `flatpak override` lines (user installation).
# One line per app. First field = Flatpak ref (e.g. com.valvesoftware.Steam); remaining fields = args to `flatpak override --user`.
# Lines starting with # are ignored. Apply: main provision pass in apply-atomic-provision.sh (after install/update).
# Security: use least privilege. Example below is commented out — only enable with eyes open.
# com.valvesoftware.Steam --filesystem=host
